  <brief_title>Vinorelbine/Gemcitabine Versus Vinorelbine/Carboplatin in Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Vinorelbine Plus Gemcitabine (VG) Versus Vinorelbine Plus Carboplatin (VC) in Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer. An Open Randomized Multicenter Phase III Trial From Norwegian Lung Cancer Study Group (NLCG)</official_title>
