  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to explore if the combination of vinorelbine and gemcitabine is
      better than vinorelbine and carboplatin in the treatment of advanced non-small cell lung
      cancer, in terms of survival, quality of life and need for palliative radiotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
